verage; no external service, Docker image, system property, or library-specific extra dependency is required.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The artifact declares optional com.github.jnr:jnr-unixsocket for Unix socket fallback, but on JDK 21 fs2 uses the JDK Unix-domain-socket implementation, so do not add jnr-unixsocket unless explicitly testing the fallback path.\",\n    \"Network and TLS tests should remain self-contained with localhost/in-process servers or JDK TLS/key-store APIs; relying on external endpoints would be unnecessary and brittle.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c1efea4e79d964d016a28d0039afc81949c6d63b23bc7cf45\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3425, "output": 701, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 31774, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781059570499, "responseId": "resp_0c1efea4e79d964d016a28cff47f688194a119e02b315b45b7"}}
